<bibRefCitation id="EFBF4B2FCD05FFE2FE4F4C6FB162FECC" author="Kaas" box="[424,544,260,284]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" refString="Kaas, P. (1991) Mollusca, Polyplacophora: Deep-water chitons from New Caledonia. In: Resultats des Campagnes Musorstom, Vo l u m e 7. Memoires du Museum national d'Histoire Naturelle, 150, 9 - 27." type="journal article" year="1991">
